# YouTube Browser Extensions

Extensions to enhance, control, and declutter your YouTube experience.

---

## 1. Video Speed Controller `v0.10.2`

**Purpose:** Speed up, slow down, advance, and rewind HTML5 audio/video with keyboard shortcuts.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Chrome/Brave** | [Video Speed Controller on Chrome Web Store](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/video-speed-controller/nffaoalbilbmmfgbnbgppjihopabppdk) |
| **Firefox** | [Video Speed Controller on Firefox Add-ons](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/videospeed/) |

**Key Features:**
- Works on any HTML5 video — YouTube, Netflix, Udemy, etc.
- Keyboard shortcuts to increase/decrease speed on the fly
- Fine-grained speed control (e.g. 1.1x, 1.75x, 2.5x)
- Rewind and advance by seconds with hotkeys

