## 2. Zoom to Fill — Ultrawide Video `v2.2.1`

**Purpose:** Remove black bars on Netflix, Amazon Prime, Disney Plus, HBO Max, and YouTube by changing to ultrawide video aspect ratio.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Chrome/Brave** | [Zoom to Fill on Chrome Web Store](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/zoom-to-fill-ultrawide-vi/adpjjimagbjfglkodpofgfphpbdlfeiho) |
| **Firefox** | Not officially listed; use on a Chromium-based browser |

**Key Features:**
- Removes black bars from ultrawide monitor users
- Works on YouTube, Netflix, Amazon Prime, Disney+, HBO Max
- Adjusts video aspect ratio to fill the screen
- One-click toggle

