## 3. AutoPause `v2.9.1`

**Purpose:** Pause other audio and video sources automatically if audio is playing on the active tab, with automatic resume.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Chrome/Brave** | [AutoPause on Chrome Web Store](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/autopause/bcecidolamfbkgokgpnlpmhjcgjlhli) |
| **Firefox** | [AutoPause on Firefox Add-ons](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/autopause) |

**Key Features:**
- Auto-pauses background tabs when a new video/audio starts
- Resumes paused tabs when current tab stops playing
- Prevents multiple tabs from playing audio simultaneously
- Great for multitasking across YouTube, Spotify, etc.

