## 5. Unhook — Remove YouTube Recommendations `v1.6.9`

**Purpose:** Hide YouTube distractions — related videos, shorts, comments, suggestions wall, homepage feed, trending, and more.

| | |
|---|---|
| **Chrome/Brave** | [Unhook on Chrome Web Store](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/unhook-remove-youtube-rec/khncfooichmfbepaaaebnommgaepoid) |
| **Firefox** | [Unhook on Firefox Add-ons](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/unhook-youtube/) |

**Key Features:**
- Hide homepage feed, recommended sidebar, end cards
- Remove Shorts, trending, comments, and autoplay
- Toggle each element independently
- Great for focused study/work sessions without rabbit holes

